-- V31 — catalog enrichment.
--   1. Fill 355 previously-empty default prices (market hints from rabotniki.ua,
--      fuzzy-matched within trade; estimated by unit where no direct match). Guarded on
--      suggested_price = 0 so a real price is never overwritten. Only the DEFAULT catalog
--      is touched — a master's own catalog_items (copied by value) keep their edits.
--   2. Add 62 new default positions at added_in_version = 2, so existing masters
--      see them under "Add new from library" (currentVersion = MAX(added_in_version)).
--   3. Expand + extend the default estimate templates (more positions each + new bundles).

